like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:44:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>車都係得3隊抽姐，疤,psg,比錫達斯</blockquote><br />\n其實想問一問，因為呢啲情況到抽籤嗰陣會唔會車呢d隊抽先？</blockquote><br />\n我估一係其他隊照抽先，如果抽剩比疤鈀是旦一隊但未到車就直接宣佈車對呢隊？<br />\n一係就車抽先但如果一早已經知道果啲波係果三隊好似有啲唔妥，有無人知始終第一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4575399205ab4f8da95a2f8783639799ccc2d18","tid":491933,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:47:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想睇比錫達斯可以行到幾遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多左個比比真係勁咁多咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔關佢事 係勁在哥利斯馬/巴布/Talisca/杜辛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2741bcc1dc9c7528f018e20c81880831b39b003","tid":491933,"uid":14806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:52:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想睇比錫達斯可以行到幾遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多左個比比真係勁咁多咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔關佢事 係勁在哥利斯馬/巴布/Talisca/杜辛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有尼格度 加利美度 <br />\n全部過哂高峰 不過一拼歐聯之力仲有既 <br />\n而且比比穏定後防 唔多唔少令隊波更加穩定"},{"pid":"c451b508dc1b7d982ca868faee34f2ebbf786aa2","tid":491933,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:56:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴黎對皇馬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴黎vs祖</blockquote><br />\n尼馬vs大巴拿"},{"pid":"ba84276c50595ffb2aa9bd188ff5247b6bbbcabf","tid":491933,"uid":126524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T08:57:15.000Z","msg":"幾時抽籤？"},{"pid":"4c879bd58cca5f8a2e354f508b422c3e44eae478","tid":491933,"uid":115150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit